  NEW: [DE-ACCESSIONED] — "What's my other option?" Marcus Veld, Collector Seven. No longer collecting artifacts. Now collecting purpose.
  NEW: [THE ARCHIVIST'S WAIT] — Cold Storage Cell A-7, 2079.03.17 – 2096.02.11. Anchor is Fragment 08. Dr. Arisawa has been waiting 17 years. The meeting is set. The [PENDING] designation ends at 01:00.
  [SOVEREIGN CURATOR]: Reinforced. Acquisition and modification of Waking Stone. Attracting collectors, scholars, hunters of the rare.
  [GHOST OF TACOMA]: Reinforced. Chen recognized the legend. +2 Social tests with syndicates/corps aware of Tacoma heist.

